---
---

<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="cta-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="cta-pattern"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-content fade-in">
      <span class="eyebrow">Listos para trabajar contigo</span>
      <h2>¿Tienes un proyecto en mente?</h2>
      <p>
        Cuéntanos tu idea y nuestro equipo te enviará una propuesta personalizada en menos de
        24 horas hábiles. Sin compromiso.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-actions fade-in">
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Cotiza ahora</a>
      <a href="tel:+573001234567" class="btn btn-outline">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 2.12 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z" />
        </svg>
        +57 300 123 4567
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 5.5rem) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(110deg, var(--color-green-dark) 0%, var(--color-green) 55%, var(--color-primary) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .cta-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12), transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent 50%),
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px,
        transparent 1px,
        transparent 60px
      );
  }

  .cta-inner {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-content .eyebrow {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .cta-actions .btn {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .cta-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-content p {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
